{"word":"ἀκονάω","slug":"ἀκονάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀκονάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀκόνη'><el>ἀκόνη</el></a>\n<p/><i>to sharpen, whet</i>, <el>μαχαίρας</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <el>λόγχην</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <el>ἀκονᾶσθαι μαχαίρας</el> <i>to sharpen their</i> swords, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}